name: GraphCast
description: AI-based medium-range weather forecasting model. Pre-trained on ERA5 data from 1979 to 2017 and fine-tuned on HRES data from 2016 to 2021.
architecture: Graph neural network based on an “encode-process-decode” configuration.
training_data: Pre-trained on ERA5 data from 1979 to 2017 and fine-tuned on HRES data from 2016 to 2021.
